# Daily downloads with windowed formulas — each result column SPILLS down from its top cell.
# movingavg/rollingmax need a full window (#N/A until then); cumsum runs the total from day one.
Day	Downloads	3-day avg	3-day max	Running total
Mon	120	=movingavg(B2:B8, 3)	=rollingmax(B2:B8, 3)	=cumsum(B2:B8)
Tue	135
Wed	150
Thu	144
Fri	180
Sat	96
Sun	111
